modelVersions.description:
This Model is aiming at mid-real 2.5d likeness. Re-did it from my older Model epi_2.5Dphotogodess whis is based on the realism model and mixed with different Models in different weights.

Mostly Clip Skip 2 gives best looking results and Hi-Res fix should be used for detailed looking results.

Reviews are very welcome 👍
Whish you much fun with that model ❤
